{"claim_type": "measurement", "line_end": 64, "line_start": 64, "page_hint": null, "section": "PROGRAM", "text": "Rod specimens were machined from cast blanks and annealed at $2150^{\\circ}\\mathrm{F}$ for 1 hr/in. of thickness."}
